data.description:
Welcome to the Sun Valley Estates in Lakewood, where this captivating 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home awaits you. With 2,680 finished square feet on a generous 7,393 square foot lot, this property offers both space and comfort.

Nestled in this vibrant community, you'll enjoy the convenience of Belmar Park and Addenbrooke Parks just a stone's throw away. Plus, easy access to 6th avenue ensures you can quickly reach both the mountains and downtown Denver.

This home is adorned with numerous features, including stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and an abundance of kitchen cabinets, a large pantry, and vaulted ceilings. The open floor plan is accentuated by beautiful wood beams on the ceiling, and you'll find tile and wood floors throughout the house. Large family room with built-in shelving,
gas fireplace, and wet bar. The private backyard boasts mature landscaping and a covered patio with an extended patio and pergola, perfect for outdoor gatherings.

Notably, this home comes equipped with an air conditioner, recently replaced solar panels with 9 years remaining on the lease, and a brand new roof. Additionally, there are 2 huge sheds on the property, one of which even has a garage door to store tools and motorcycles.

The interior is a blank canvas, ready for your personal touch. Make it your own, and let your creativity flow.

This home's outdoor space is great for hosting friends and family, providing the ideal backdrop for creating lasting memories.

This property is perfect for families searching for a place to make great memories. Don't miss the opportunity to call this charming Lakewood house your home, as it won't stay on the market for long!
